Achievements.Name: War Hero
Achievements.Description: All missions of the single player campaign completed.

Achievements.Name: Nice Collection
Achievements.Description: Unlock 65% of the planes in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Complete Collection
Achievements.Description: Unlock all the planes in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Great Streak
Achievements.Description: Make a killing streak of at least 12 kills.

Achievements.Name: Eye in the Back
Achievements.Description: Successfully use defensive weapons 50 times over the course of the campaign.

Achievements.Name: Strategist
Achievements.Description: Your wingmen score at least 50 kills over the course of the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Completist
Achievements.Description: Accomplish all secondary objectives in all the single player campaign missions.

Achievements.Name: Ace
Achievements.Description: Obtain the Ace rating in at least 5 missions of the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Ace for a Day
Achievements.Description: Obtain the Ace rating in at least one mission of the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Well Covered
Achievements.Description: Your turret gunners score 15 kills in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Tech Sawy
Achievements.Description: Acquire at least two technological advancements in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Tech Expert
Achievements.Description: Acquire all technological advancements in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Showoff
Achievements.Description: Perform at least 25 stunts in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Skirmish Explored
Achievements.Description: Reach 25% in all skirmish missions in the coop mode.

Achievements.Name: Skirmish Advanced
Achievements.Description: Reach 50% in at least three skirmish missions in the coop mode.

Achievements.Name: Skirmish Perfected
Achievements.Description: Reach 100% in at least two skirmish missions in the coop mode.

Achievements.Name: Healthy Finish
Achievements.Description: Finish a solo multiplayer match without being last on the table.

Achievements.Name: Good Finish
Achievements.Description: Finish a solo multiplayer match above mid-table.

Achievements.Name: Top Finish
Achievements.Description: Finish a solo multiplayer match on the top of the table.

Achievements.Name: Team Player
Achievements.Description: Respond to at least 25 requests from teammates in multiplayer.

Achievements.Name: Streak Master
Achievements.Description: Make three killing streaks of at least 15 kills.

Achievements.Name: Curiosity Satisfied
Achievements.Description: Play at least one match in every multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Versatile Pilot
Achievements.Description: Achieve multiplayer kills with at least 15 types of different aircraft.

Achievements.Name: Dominator
Achievements.Description: Make 15 kills in a row without dying, in a multiplayer match.

Achievements.Name: Good Team Play
Achievements.Description: Be part of the winning team in 3 squad matches.

Achievements.Name: Excellent Team Play
Achievements.Description: Be part of the winning team in 25 squad matches.

Achievements.Name: Superb Team Play
Achievements.Description: Be part of the winning team in 50 squad matches.

Achievements.Name: Proven Pilot
Achievements.Description: Make 50 kills in adversarial multiplayer matches.

Achievements.Name: Skilled Dogfighter
Achievements.Description: Make 150 kills in adversarial multiplayer matches.

Achievements.Name: Ace of Aces
Achievements.Description: Make 300 kills in adversarial multiplayer matches.

Achievements.Name: Veteran
Achievements.Description: Play 25 hours online, in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Hardened Veteran
Achievements.Description: Play 50 hours online, in any multiplayer mode.
